# Run your function locally with `func start host`
@baseUrl = http://localhost:7071/api
@sessionId = "123e4567-0001"

### 1) Missing user_msg (should return 400 Bad Request)
GET {{baseUrl}}/chat

### 2) Send chat message via POST
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat?sessionId={{sessionId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "user_msg": "How are you doing today?"
}

### 3) Send chat message via GET
GET {{baseUrl}}/chat?sessionId={{sessionId}}&user_msg="How are you doing today?"

### 4) Another conversation turn via POST
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat?sessionId={{sessionId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "user_msg": "Adding new conversation history to Azure Cosmos DB."
}